skdetail:

Invocation Name: d. n. s. tools
des: You can use DNS Tools to convert between IP addresses and domain names by saying give me the IP for domain. Some examples are give me the i. p. for google dot com and give me the domain for eight dot eight dot eight dot eight.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
